M5 ships are scout ships. They are the lightest vessels flying in known space. Whilst they are armed, this armament is little more than token; these ships are no match for any other class in a fight, including armed TS-class ships.

They are designed and usually used for reconnaissance and anti-recon, or sometimes as cannon fodder. Some M5s are referred to as the 'rich man's [[fighter drone]]'.

The most powerful [[Commonwealth]] M5 weapon is generally the [[Particle Accelerator Cannon]], but some can't mount those and have to cope with the weaker [[Impulse Ray Emitter]].

[[Terran]] M5's are limited to only the [[Electro-Magnetic Plasma Cannon]], which is both a blessing (for its damage, range and energy efficiency) and a curse (due to its low projectile speed).

